    <aura:description>
    A complex component with extensive opportunities for testing.

    This is a presentation component that contains view logic without have direct dependency on Lighting Data Service (LDS). This pattern explores ways to decouple presentation logic from server/integration logic.

    Some of the decoupling illustrated is necessary because LDS can currently only be used inside Lightning Experience. (This is a documented limitation of the LDS beta.)
    </aura:description>
